import React from 'react'
import { Form, Button, FormControl } from "react-bootstrap";


function Service({ image, count, key }) {
  
  return (
    <Form>
      <Form.Group> 
        <Form.Label className="sr-only">Service</Form.Label>
         {/* how are we storing   */}
        <Form.Control as="select">
          <option>1</option>
          <option>2</option>
        </Form.Control>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group>
        <Form.Label>Image</Form.Label>

      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group>
        <Form.Label>Description</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control as="textarea" className="m-auto" rows="3"/>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group>
        <Form.Label>Rate</Form.Label>
          <Form.Control plaintext type="text" placeholder={count} />
      </Form.Group>
      <Button hidden type="submit">
        Save
      </Button>
    </Form>
    );
}

export default Service;
